整咗個汁，然後用paprika當孜然粉咁放上面焗。<br />\n<br />\n用西式材料整嘅土匪，咁咪即係海盜囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T16:13:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇食譜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:04:02.000Z","msg":"茄汁：3湯匙<br />\n麥芽糖：1-2湯匙<br />\n辣椒仔：適量<br />\n生抽：少少<br />\n黑椒：半湯匙<br />\n糖：一湯匙<br />\n鹽：兩茶匙<br />\n蒜：三粒(剁蓉)<br />\n蔥頭：兩粒(剁蓉)<br />\n<br />\n徹底撈匀晒(特別係啲麥芽糖) 後，拎啲雞翼去醃一晚。<br />\n<br />\n第二日拎去焗(預熱180度，上火焗15分鐘)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/130052_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F130052_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0e4d0f11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n焗好之後拎出嚟，掃一層汁，再焗多5-10分鐘，重覆2-3次。<br />\n<br />\n之後，如果中意食paprika，就拎啲雞翼出嚟，冚一層paprika響面，焗多5分鐘，食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(唔中意就算，直接食都好味)"},{"pid":"89d79b49d99a2e68650d8bd2e696ee612e28cbcb","tid":779691,"uid":105779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20845e0d7f7f507669d424ff32a92eb2462e6f61","tid":779691,"uid":33004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T15:20:12.000Z","msg":"肉jer意粉整得幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T09:49:54.000Z","msg":"有人夾錢，啲料梗係用足啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成包芝士+勁多肉醬，實靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf607ca4871df46643011f2d8e40380d41a5240","tid":779691,"uid":6275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T09:51:58.000Z","msg":"無麥芽糖用蜜糖得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla